description: Try our easy to follow Vegetable Soup With Pumpkin Seeds recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Vegetable Soup With Pumpkin Seeds Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Peel & slice pumpkin, leek, celery root. Add into a pot of 500ml boiling water. Place 1 Vegeta Chicken Stock Cube & cook all ingredients for about 10 minutes.
Remove from heat, allow to cool for a few minutes. Add to the blender with celery leaves & blend together until smooth.
Serve the prepared soup in a bowl, drizzled with pumpkin oil & sprinkle with pumpkin seeds.
